-CategorieOrganisation-242\"> </a></td><td>Unité hospitalière de chirurgie plastique, reconstructrice et esthétique</td><td/><td/><td>2025-01-31T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-01-31T12:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td/><td>active</td></tr><tr style=\"background-color: #ffeeee\"><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">243<a name=\"TRE-R244-CategorieOrganisation-243\"> </a></td><td>Cabinet de ville de médecine intensive et réanimation (MIR)</td><td/><td>Déprécié</td><td>2025-01-31T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-08-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-08-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-08-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>deprecated</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">244<a name=\"TRE-R244-CategorieOrganisation-244\"> </a></td><td>Equipe Mobile d'Expertise en Réadaptation (EMER) neuro-locomoteur</td><td/><td/><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td/><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">245<a name=\"TRE-R244-CategorieOrganisation-245\"> </a></td><td>Centre expert en maladies rares</td><td/><td/><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td/><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">246<a name=\"TRE-R244-CategorieOrganisation-246\"> </a></td><td>Service d'Aide Médicale Urgente (SAMU)</td><td/><td/><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td/><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">247<a name=\"TRE-R244-CategorieOrganisation-247\"> </a></td><td>Structure Mobile d'Urgence et de Réanimation (SMUR)</td><td/><td/><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td/><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">248<a name=\"TRE-R244-CategorieOrganisation-248\"> </a></td><td>Unité de biologie</td><td/><td/><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td>2025-03-28T12:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td/><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">249<a name=\"TRE-R244-CategorieOrganisation-249\"> </a></td><td>Unité de Soins d